{PARA 11 "" 1 "" {XPPMATH 20 "6#>%$eq6G/%\"yG,&%\"xG\"\"\"\"\"%!\"\"" 
}}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 25 "solve( \{eq5,eq6\}, \{x,y
\});" }}{PARA 11 "" 1 "" {XPPMATH 20 "6$<$/%\"xG\"\"#/%\"yG!\"#<$/F%F)
/F(!\"'" }}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 42 "eq7:=x^2+y^2 = 1
6;  eq8:=x^2/36+y^2/4 = 1;" }}{PARA 11 "" 1 "" {XPPMATH 20 "6#>%$eq7G/
,&*$)%\"xG\"\"#\"\"\"F+*$)%\"yGF*F+F+\"#;" }}{PARA 11 "" 1 "" 
{XPPMATH 20 "6#>%$eq8G/,&*&\"#O!\"\"%\"xG\"\"#\"\"\"*&\"\"%F)%\"yGF+F,
F," }}}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 25 "solve( \{eq7,eq8\}, \+
