" {TEXT -1 13 "1.  The fact " }{TEXT 303 121 "If there is a Binomial (
a+b)^4 then that means (a+b)(a+b)(a+b)(a+b) which results in a^4 + 4a^
3b + 6a^2b^2 + 4a b^3 + b^4" }{TEXT -1 45 "  is true, but what is the \+
Binomial Theorem??" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 43 "   The problem aske
d you to find the sums  " }{XPPEDIT 18 0 "sum(binomial(n,k),k = 0 .. n
)" "6#-%$sumG6$-%)binomialG6$%\"nG%\"kG/F*;\"\"!F)" }{TEXT -1 26 "   f
or n = 1, 2, 3,   etc." }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 
0 "" {TEXT -1 8 "2.  Done" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 42 "3.  What was
 your answer to the question  " }{TEXT 304 88 "Why did we need to incl
ude the ,x in the solve command in order to find the roots of p3?" }
{TEXT -1 81 "  ??\n4.  Done\n5.  What happend on b.??\n\n1.  1.5\n2.  \+
4\n3.  3\n4.  4\n5.  3.5\n\n16/20\n" }}}{MARK "0 0" 0 }{VIEWOPTS 1 1 
